# Never commit local Terraform state (it can contain secrets: certs, tokens)
# or the provider cache. State here is ephemeral by design (see versions.tf).
# Note: .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored - it pins provider
# hashes so `terraform init` is reproducible. That file gets committed.
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
crash.log
